<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.286219>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Rhampholeon tiburyi sp. nov.: A—Allotype (PEM R 17132, K. A. Tolley); B—Paratype (PEM R 17134, K Tolley); C—Head of male paratype (PEM R 20372) showing snout flexure; D—Preserved female holotype (PEM R 14921); E—Manho Forest, Mt. Namuli (J. Bayliss)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/286219/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.286220>
